  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the grill to medium-high heat.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together olive oil, garlic, cumin, coriander, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Add the lamb cubes to the bowl and toss to coat with the marinade.",
    "Thread the lamb cubes onto skewers, leaving a small space between each piece.",
    "Grill the kebabs for 8-10 minutes, turning occasionally, until the lamb is cooked through.",
    "Meanwhile, prepare the fermented turnip by mixing it with orange zest in a small bowl.",
    "Serve the kebabs in a bento box with the fermented turnip and orange zest mixture on the side.",
    "Garnish with fresh parsley or cilantro, if desired."
  ],
